<p class="ayah 24-24" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَوْمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(On a) Day,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَشْهَدُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will bear witness</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">against them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَلْسِنَتُهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their tongues,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَيْدِيهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and their hands</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَرْجُلُهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and their feet</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they used</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَعْمَلُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to) do.</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/24:24" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="2815"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>24<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></a></p>
