<p class="ayah 24-27" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">O you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believe!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(Do) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَدْخُلُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">enter</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بُيُوتًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">houses</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">غَيْرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">other (than)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بُيُوتِكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your houses</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَتَّىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">until</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَسْتَأْنِسُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you have asked permission</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَتُسَلِّمُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and you have greeted</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[on]</span></span><span cl